      • getDate

        LocalDate getDate()
        Gets the date of the curve node.

        This is the date that the node on the curve is defined as. There is not necessarily a direct relationship with a date from an underlying instrument. It may be the effective date or the maturity date but equally it may not.

        Returns:
        the date
